{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"id143e4924-3a70-11f1-b089-c1e1e512a22d","identifier":"/us/usc/t21/s361"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"361"},"text":"§ 361.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Adulterated cosmetics","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"A cosmetic shall be deemed to be adulterated—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id143e4925-3a70-11f1-b089-c1e1e512a22d","identifier":"/us/usc/t21/s361/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" If it bears or contains any poisonous or deleterious substance which may render it injurious to users under the conditions of use prescribed in the labeling thereof, or under such conditions of use as are customary or usual, except that this provision shall not apply to coal-tar hair dye, the label of which bears the following legend conspicuously displayed thereon: “Caution—This product contains ingredients which may cause skin irritation on certain individuals and a preliminary test according to accompanying directions should first be made. This product must not be used for dyeing the eyelashes or eyebrows; to do so may cause blindness.”, and the labeling of which bears adequate directions for such preliminary testing. For the purposes of this paragraph and paragraph (e) the term “hair dye” shall not include eyelash dyes or eyebrow dyes.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id143e4926-3a70-11f1-b089-c1e1e512a22d","identifier":"/us/usc/t21/s361/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" If it consists in whole or in part of any filthy, putrid, or decomposed substance.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id143e4927-3a70-11f1-b089-c1e1e512a22d","identifier":"/us/usc/t21/s361/c"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"c"},"text":"(c)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" If it has been prepared, packed, or held under insanitary conditions whereby it may have become contaminated with filth, or whereby it may have been rendered injurious to health.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id143e4928-3a70-11f1-b089-c1e1e512a22d","identifier":"/us/usc/t21/s361/d"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"d"},"text":"(d)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" If its container is composed, in whole or in part, of any poisonous or deleterious substance which may render the contents injurious to health.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id143e4929-3a70-11f1-b089-c1e1e512a22d","identifier":"/us/usc/t21/s361/e"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"e"},"text":"(e)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" If it is not a hair dye and it is, or it bears or contains, a color additive which is unsafe within the meaning of ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t21/s379e/a"},"text":"section 379e(a) of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id143e492a-3a70-11f1-b089-c1e1e512a22d","identifier":"/us/usc/t21/s361/f"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"f"},"text":"(f)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" If it has been manufactured or processed under conditions that do not meet the good manufacturing practice requirements of ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t21/s364b"},"text":"section 364b of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id143e492b-3a70-11f1-b089-c1e1e512a22d","identifier":"/us/usc/t21/s361/g"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"g"},"text":"(g)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" If it is a cosmetic product, and the cosmetic product, including each ingredient in the cosmetic product, does not have adequate substantiation for ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"idref":"fn002092"},"text":"1","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"type":"footnote","id":"fn002092"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{},"text":"1","children":[],"tail":" So in original. Probably should be “of”."}],"tail":" safety, as defined in "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t21/s364d/c"},"text":"section 364d(c) of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"id1440b92c-3a70-11f1-b089-c1e1e512a22d"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1938-06-25/ch675/s601"},"text":"June 25, 1938, ch. 675, § 601","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/52/1054"},"text":"52 Stat. 1054","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/86/618/tI/s102/c/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 86–618, title I, § 102(c)(1)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1960-07-12"},"text":"July 12, 1960","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/74/398"},"text":"74 Stat. 398","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/102/571/tI/s107/11"},"text":"Pub. L. 102–571, title I, § 107(11)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1992-10-29"},"text":"Oct. 29, 1992","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/106/4499"},"text":"106 Stat. 4499","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/103/80/s3/x"},"text":"Pub. L. 103–80, § 3(x)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1993-08-13"},"text":"Aug. 13, 1993","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/107/778"},"text":"107 Stat. 778","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/117/328/dFF/tIII/s3503/a/2"},"text":"Pub. L. 117–328, div. FF, title III, § 3503(a)(2)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2022-12-29"},"text":"Dec. 29, 2022","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/136/5858"},"text":"136 Stat. 5858","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"id1440b92d-3a70-11f1-b089-c1e1e512a22d"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"id1440b92e-3a70-11f1-b089-c1e1e512a22d"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"amendments","id":"id1440b92f-3a70-11f1-b089-c1e1e512a22d"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Amendments","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2022—Subsecs. (f), (g). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/117/328"},"text":"Pub. L. 117–328","children":[],"tail":" added subsecs. (f) and (g)."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1993—Subsec. (a). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/103/80"},"text":"Pub. L. 103–80","children":[],"tail":" substituted “usual, except that this” for “usual: "},{"tag":"i","attrib":{},"text":"Provided","children":[],"tail":", That this”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1992—Par. (e). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/102/571"},"text":"Pub. L. 102–571","children":[],"tail":" substituted “379e(a)” for “376(a)”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1960—Par. (e). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/86/618"},"text":"Pub. L. 86–618","children":[],"tail":" substituted “and it is, or it bears or contains, a color additive which is unsafe within the meaning of "},{"tag":"ref","attrib"